examples.en: The dog has chewed up my new shoes!
Nina chewed her lower lip anxiously.
examples.ru: Из-за тревоги Нина кусала свою нижнюю губу.

examples.en: A mouse chewed through the cord.
That confounded dog chewed up my shoe.
examples.ru: Эта чёртова собака сжевала мой ботинок.

examples.en: The dog's chewed up my slippers again.
